<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/49001AHJBVTCVBRMRMLMCJSNSSQLBRQJR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2025-26 DAN School Wind Ensemble";
  schema:description """
	The Queen’s University Wind Ensemble, directed by Dan Tremblay, will certainly resonate well in the beautiful acoustics of the Isabel concert hall. Compositional works by corner stone composers Holst and Malcom Arnold radiate with melancholic folk energy while Persichetti’s Psalm, Gjeilo’s Serenity, and Ticheli’s Rest transcend tranquility and ethereal stillness.
""";
