<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/47801AQSJJVSSQJNMDHJPPGNDTMSTPTST> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2025-26 Good Lovelies Christmas Concert";
  schema:description """
	The Good Lovelies’ much-loved Christmas tour returns this December, bringing holiday classics, winter favourites and a sprinkle of the band’s original songs that you’ve come to love.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Caroline Brooks, Kerri Ough, and Susan Passmore are JUNO award-winning songwriters and multi-instrumentalists, known for their rich harmonies and nostalgic sound. Blending folk-roots, old-time swing, bluegrass, pop, and soul, their music is a perfect fit for the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>They are joined by their Merry Men, a trio of world class musicians: Robbie Grunwald on keys, Steve Zsirai on bass and Mark Mariash on drums.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With great harmonies, stories and songs that will have you humming all the way home, the Good Lovelies’ holiday concert is a truly cup-filling evening for anyone who loves the magic of the season.
""";
