<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/46801ACDBKCSKJDBSGRJBRPHCJBLCKVCG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2025-26 Isabel Voices: A Festive Celebration";
  schema:description """
	Our beloved candlelit concert returns. Join us and bask in the warm glow as voices, harp, string ensemble, and piano unite in a radiant program that weaves together winter stillness, warmth, and light—capturing the true spirit of the season. This gorgeous repertoire includes “The Road” by Ola Gjeilo, featuring string orchestra, piano and harp, a beautiful setting of “In the Bleak Mid Winter” by Dan Forrest, and “By Night” by Elaine Hagenberg. Featuring the virtuosic playing of guest harpist, Caroline Leonardelli. Complimentary seasonal refreshments will be offered.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Livestream Tickets are available at the link above.  Livestream Season Passes are also available, <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/ticketing/livestream-season-pass-2025--26\">here</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To complete your Isabel Voices 2025-26 Season Pass, select seats for all three Isabel Voices events and discount will automatically apply at checkout. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This event is supported by <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.queensu.ca/theisabel/rent-isabel/ballytobin-foundation\">The Ballytobin Foundation</a>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-11-29T14:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
