<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/40201AJMHGMLBHTGVNKHNPGVSVHHPSMBQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Miss Emily Christmas";
  schema:description """
	Throughout Emily Fennell’s career as a singer, songwriter, and performer, the Christmas season has always been a time that unites her favourite themes—community, generational love, and family. A Miss Emily Christmas combines sleigh rides and candy canes with soul music and glittery pink accents. It’s a fun and welcoming celebration that will have you up on your feet singing along and sharing the best that the season has to offer.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: Only tickets purchased directly from the Isabel Box Office or the Isabel Website will be valid for performances presented by the Isabel Bader Centre for the Performing Arts.
""";
