<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/47401AKQNQDVQMQKDSCQGTCTQNHNCHLHR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Night on Broadway";
  schema:description """
	After our sold-out, show-stopping performances in 2024 and 2025, The Isabel Voices returns with not one, but two dazzling shows! Don’t miss this high-energy celebration of Broadway’s biggest hits—right here in Kingston. A 15-piece band, along with exceptional singing and dancing, brings alive repertoire such as, \"On Broadway\" from \"Beautiful, The Musical,\" and \"Phantom of the Opera Medley\" from Phantom of the Opera, with selections from \"The Great Gatsby.\"<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Livestream Tickets are available at the link above.  Livestream Season Passes are also available, <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/ticketing/livestream-season-pass-2025--26\">here</a>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To complete your Isabel Voices 2025-26 Season Pass, select seats for all three Isabel Voices events and discount will automatically apply at checkout. 
""";
