<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/40601AVRVRQNNTTMJRHQKDLRCKSKHBGKP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bridge & Wolak - 'Scandalous Romantics' ";
  schema:description """
	Genius! Stardom! Betrayal! Scandalous Romantics is a hilarious tabloid take on stories behind the most celebrated music stars across genres—and their spectacular lapses in judgement! Co-written with CBC’s Tom Allen, this family-friendly show tells stories around some of the greatest music ever written. Michael Bridge, digital accordion, and Kornel Wolak, clarinet and piano, dazzle with virtuosity, down-to-earth humour, and their original arrangements in a fun program steeped in contemporary culture.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: Only tickets purchased directly from the Isabel Box Office or the Isabel Website will be valid for performances presented by the Isabel Bader Centre for the Performing Arts.
""";
