<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/58401ABJPVQMJDTRSGPPTQCLRCSRLSTSQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "In the Key of Blue";
  schema:description """
	Jarod Scott dreams of becoming the next big thing on the Canadian Rock Scene. Jarod’s break seems to come when a prominent MP invites the band to perform at an election rally being televised by the CBC. The national stage seems grand, but when the road to fame presents a few potholes, Jarod’s life takes on significant damage. He looks to one of the few friends he has left to piece his life back together. With the classic music of preeminent rockers Blue Rodeo punctuating the plot, the characters of “In the Key of Blue” navigate the perils of trust and lies.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Welcome to In The Key of Blue</span><span><br/></span>A New Canadian Musical, Born and Raised in Prince Edward County, Starring Miss Emily and showcasing the talent of The County. Featuring the iconic music of Blue Rodeo, a story of dreams, love, and betrayal.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>VIP Package<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Each VIP Package includes 1 seat for the show, a Prince Edward County Community Swag Bag, VIP access to the Lounge before the show, during intermission and after show wind down. Plus lots of other goodies to help you enjoy the experience. The perfect compliment to the evening.<span><br/></span>$100, plus HST & ticketing fee<span><br/></span>To purchase a VIP Package, Select \"VIP Package\" Ticket Type when choosing your seats. 
""";
