<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/52801ANDDVVVVLHPQNVDLNNNCBBSTGNKP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Keith Whiteduck";
  schema:description """
	Sudbury-born Anishinaabe artist and musician Keith Whiteduck is a Cambrian College graduate whose genre-blending artistry draws on classical training, rock, jazz, and Indigenous influences. This concert features music from his album Enter Keith Whiteduck alongside new original works and an eclectic range of covers, from Beethoven and Chopin to Oscar Peterson, Bob Dylan, and the Grateful Dead. Bold, expressive, and deeply personal, his performances move seamlessly across styles while remaining unmistakably his own.
""";
