<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/53201AKJTJLSKDPDLPTMDVPTDGSNGNBPL> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "National Youth Orchestra of Canada";
  schema:description """
	Experience the next generation of Canadian musical talent with the National Youth Orchestra of Canada, where young musicians from across the country come together to perform world-class repertoire with passion and precision. The wide-ranging program spans Anna Clyne’s vibrant <span class=\"ItalicText\">Masquerade</span>, Lilli Boulanger’s <span class=\"ItalicText\">D’un soir Trista</span>, a featured concerto showcase, and Sergei Prokofiev’s powerful Symphony No. 5 in B-flat major.
""";
