<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/56402ANHKDSKJGKVPHVHRBPTSSQLKHDTK> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Rob Kapilow with Gryphon Trio";
  schema:description """
	Join composer and commentator Rob Kapilow for his acclaimed “What Makes It Great?” program, an engaging deep dive into the music of Ludwig van Beethoven. With infectious enthusiasm and remarkable clarity, Kapilow unpacks Beethoven’s genius in the famous “Archduke Trio”, revealing the ideas and emotions behind the notes in ways that transform how you listen. Featuring live performances by the Gryphon Trio, this illuminating and entertaining evening invites both devoted classical fans and curious newcomers to experience Beethoven’s music with fresh ears.
""";
