<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/55201ACQGLDNVCCMPJHCCRNVTBRTNQTQG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Royal Conservatory Orchestra";
  schema:description """
	The Royal Conservatory Orchestra is one of North America’s leading training orchestras, providing Glenn Gould School students with professional-level rehearsal and performance experience. Under the guidance of renowned guest conductors, the orchestra performs regularly at Koerner Hall and other major venues, including a Carnegie Hall debut in 2024. Participation equips students with extensive orchestral experience, including concerto opportunities, and its graduates now play in some of the world’s top orchestras.
""";
