<http://www.spektrix.com/theisabel/event/53401ABPVVPPBPJCQVLMKKHHLLVGLBJJB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Splash’N Boots";
  schema:description """
	Canadian children’s music duo Splash’N Boots, Nick Adams (Splash) and Taes Leavitt (Boots), returns to the Isabel with their latest album, Pencil Lines. Blending folk, ska, and playful rhythms, the album explores magic, friendship, and growth. With hit shows on Treehouse TV and Disney Jr. Canada, millions of fans know their music. Their advocacy work, including Lucas’s Letters, highlights their commitment to children. Splash’N Boots are  a name to know in children’s music.
""";
